WHERE WE ALL SIT DOWN.

256
00:08:44,274 --> 00:08:45,234
ZOE:
UM, ACTUALLY, I THINK I FORGOT
SOMETHING IN MY LOCKER,

257
00:08:45,317 --> 00:08:47,569
SO I SHOULD GO.

258
00:08:47,653 --> 00:08:49,655
