FIRST DAY JITTERS,

260
00:08:54,826 --> 00:08:56,119
BUT I NEED TO START
THIS CLASS,

261
00:08:56,203 --> 00:08:58,080
SO JUST GET OVER
WHATEVER BOY DRAMA THIS IS,

262
00:08:58,163 --> 00:08:59,081
TAKE A DEEP BREATH,
CHILL OUT.

263
00:08:59,164 --> 00:09:00,374
WHY DON'T YOU
CHILL OUT?!

264
00:09:00,457 --> 00:09:01,959
(STUDENTS GASP)

265
00:09:05,254 --> 00:09:07,548
TRISTAN:
THAT REALLY IS HER
GO-TO MOVE, HUH?

266
00:09:07,631 --> 00:09:09,174
(STUDENTS CHUCKLE
AND WHISPER)

267
00:09:10,801 --> 00:09:12,302
(CARS RUMBLE)

268
00:09:19,142 --> 00:09:19,768
