ALL RIGHT,
I'M GOING TO BED.

282
00:10:08,775 --> 00:10:10,527
WHAT, WAS IT
THE VICTORY DANCE?

283
00:10:10,611 --> 00:10:12,321
IT'S THE 1:00 A.M.
THAT OKAY?

284
00:10:13,947 --> 00:10:14,907
(SIGHS HEAVILY)

285
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:17,534
WHAT?

286
00:10:17,618 --> 00:10:19,828
I JUST- I CAN'T BELIEVE
CLARE PROPOSED

287
00:10:19,912 --> 00:10:22,581
A TEXTING AND DRIVING EVENT
INSTEAD OF A DANCE.

288
00:10:22,664 --> 00:10:25,000
IT'S NICE TO KNOW ADAM'S
STILL ON PEOPLE'S MINDS.

289
00:10:25,083 --> 00:10:26,335
BUT IT'S NOT GOING
TO BRING HIM BACK, SO...

290
00:10:26,418 --> 00:10:27,920
