292
00:10:31,048 --> 00:10:32,424
(SIGHS HEAVILY)

293
00:10:32,508 --> 00:10:34,801
JUST TRY
AND GET SOME SLEEP.

294
00:10:34,885 --> 00:10:36,220
DALLAS:
YOU GONNA CRASH HERE AGAIN?

295
00:10:36,303 --> 00:10:38,180
