299
00:10:59,243 --> 00:11:00,744
(SIGHS)

300
00:11:07,209 --> 00:11:08,710
(SIGHS HEAVILY)

301
00:11:12,047 --> 00:11:13,549
(STUDENTS CHATTER)

302
00:11:17,344 --> 00:11:18,971
