YOU ARE GLOWING.

303
00:11:19,054 --> 00:11:20,973
AND WEARING
A LITTLE EXTRA MAKEUP!

304
00:11:21,056 --> 00:11:21,682
WHAT ARE YOU HIDING?

305
00:11:21,765 --> 00:11:24,059
NOTHING.

306
00:11:24,142 --> 00:11:26,520
JENNA:
WHEN DO WE GET TO KNOW WHAT KIND
OF A KISSER MIKE DALLAS IS?

307
00:11:26,603 --> 00:11:30,440
UM, IT WASN'T DALLAS.
IT WAS LEO!

308
00:11:33,652 --> 00:11:34,987
N-NO.

309
00:11:35,070 --> 00:11:37,072
YEAH, HE FLEW IN YESTERDAY.

310
00:11:37,155 --> 00:11:38,824
HE MISSED ME.
ISN'T THAT SO ROMANTIC?

311
00:11:38,907 --> 00:11:41,493
TRY INSANE!
THIS GUY CAN'T BE TRUSTED.

312
00:11:41,577 --> 00:11:43,370
THAT'S A LITTLE HARSH.

313
00:11:43,453 --> 00:11:45,414
NO. LEO HURT HER, CLARE,
PHYSICALLY!

314
00:11:45,497 --> 00:11:47,165
I SAW THE BRUISES!

315
00:11:47,249 --> 00:11:48,625
IT WAS NOTHING.

316
00:11:48,709 --> 00:11:49,334
WE GOT INTO A FIGHT,
IT GOT HEATED.

317
00:11:49,418 --> 00:11:51,336
BUT I GRABBED HIM, TOO.

318
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:53,130
STILL, ALLI,
THAT'S A WARNING SIGN.

319
00:11:53,213 --> 00:11:55,007
ALLI:
OH, LIKE DRIVING A CAR
INTO A WALL?

320
00:11:55,090 --> 00:11:56,258
OR BRINGING A GUN
TO SCHOOL?

321
00:11:56,341 --> 00:11:57,301
OR, YOU KNOW,
STEALING UNDERWEAR?

322
00:11:57,384 --> 00:11:58,802
YOUR BOYFRIENDS
AREN'T SAINTS!

323
00:11:58,886 --> 00:11:59,845
SO HE CAME HERE
JUST FOR YOU,

324
00:11:59,928 --> 00:12:01,305
WITHOUT A PLAN?

325
00:12:01,388 --> 00:12:03,515
HE CAME BECAUSE HE LOVES ME.

326
00:12:03,599 --> 00:12:05,851
WHY ARE YOU GUYS
TRYING TO RUIN THAT?

327
00:12:05,934 --> 00:12:08,353
MR. PERINO:
TODAY, WE START UNIT ONE,
THE NATURE OF POLITICS!

328
00:12:08,437 --> 00:12:09,646
BUT DREW TORRES,
YOU'LL BE MISSING OUT.

329
00:12:09,730 --> 00:12:11,231
YOU'RE WANTED IN THE OFFICE.

330
00:12:12,858 --> 00:12:13,859
WHERE'S DREW?

331
00:12:13,942 --> 00:12:15,444
(CELL PHONE BUZZES)

332
00:12:17,905 --> 00:12:19,406
(DREW GROANS)

333
00:12:22,576 --> 00:12:25,370
MORNING, B.

334
00:12:25,454 --> 00:12:27,706
BIANCA:
HEY. I DIDN'T EXPECT YOU
TO ANSWER.

335
00:12:27,789 --> 00:12:29,291
SO THEN WHY'D YOU CALL?

336
00:12:31,043 --> 00:12:31,376
