TO LEAVE YOU
A SEXY MESSAGE.

337
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:33,462
(LAUGHS)

338
00:12:33,545 --> 00:12:37,424
BIANCA:
SHOULDN'T YOU BE IN CLASS?
IT'S NINE!

339
00:12:37,508 --> 00:12:38,926
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THIS MEANS?

340
00:12:39,009 --> 00:12:40,260
