DETENTION?

341
00:12:40,344 --> 00:12:42,137
NO! NO, I FINALLY SLEPT
FOR LIKE HOURS!

342
00:12:44,890 --> 00:12:45,599
BIANCA:
YEAH, YOU FELL ASLEEP
TALKING TO ME

343
00:12:45,682 --> 00:12:46,850
ON THE PHONE
LAST NIGHT.

344
00:12:46,934 --> 00:12:49,144
WE TALKED LAST NIGHT?

345
00:12:49,228 --> 00:12:50,812
BIANCA:
AT LIKE 4:00 A.M.

346
00:12:50,896 --> 00:12:53,899
YOU WERE GROGGY.
IT WAS PRETTY CUTE.

347
00:12:53,982 --> 00:12:55,609
WHATEVER. I'M JUST GLAD
I FINALLY GOT SOME REST.

348
00:12:55,692 --> 00:12:57,194
I FEEL LIKE A NEW MAN!

349
00:12:58,862 --> 00:13:01,198
I SHOULD PROBABLY
GET TO CLASS.

350
00:13:01,281 --> 00:13:02,699
FEEL FREE TO CALL BACK
AND LEAVE THAT SEXY MESSAGE!

351
00:13:02,783 --> 00:13:04,493
BIANCA:
(SQUEALS SEXILY)

352
00:13:04,576 --> 00:13:05,494
SIMPSON:
I DON'T KNOW HOW YOU BEHAVE
ON A TV SHOW, ZOE,

353
00:13:05,577 --> 00:13:06,578
BUT WHAT YOU DID
YESTERDAY

354
00:13:06,662 --> 00:13:08,747
HAS NO PLACE
IN THE REAL WORLD!

355
00:13:08,830 --> 00:13:10,332
CAN'T YOU JUST TRANSFER ME
OUT OF THAT CLASS?

356
00:13:10,415 --> 00:13:12,835
YOU ASSAULTED A TEACHER!

357
00:13:12,918 --> 00:13:15,379
WE MAY BE TALKING
ABOUT EXPULSION.

358
00:13:15,462 --> 00:13:16,380
