DISABILITY.

359
00:13:16,463 --> 00:13:17,965
ZOE:
MOM!

360
00:13:18,382 --> 00:13:19,883
DYSLEXIA.

361
00:13:21,552 --> 00:13:23,053
IS THIS TRUE?

362
00:13:24,721 --> 00:13:26,223
ABSOLUTELY.

363
00:13:28,016 --> 00:13:30,894
ZOE, WILL YOU REQUIRE
EXTRA HELP WITH TESTS?

364
00:13:30,978 --> 00:13:32,479
NO, I WILL NOT.

365
00:13:35,482 --> 00:13:37,609
CAN I HAVE A MINUTE WITH
MY DAUGHTER, ALONE?

366
00:13:41,405 --> 00:13:42,906
I GUESS SO.

367
00:13:49,955 --> 00:13:52,332
HOW COULD YOU
TELL HIM THAT?!

368
00:13:52,416 --> 00:13:54,710
I JUST SAVED YOUR ASS!
HE WAS GONNA KICK YOU OUT!

369
00:13:54,793 --> 00:13:56,086
I WANTED HIM TO!
CAN'T YOU JUST HOME SCHOOL ME?

370
00:13:56,170 --> 00:13:57,671
NO!

371
00:13:57,754 --> 00:13:58,797
UNTIL YOU GET
ANOTHER JOB,

372
00:13:58,881 --> 00:14:00,549
I HAVE TO GET ONE
OF MY OWN.

373
00:14:00,632 --> 00:14:02,426
I'M NOT SUPPOSED
TO BE HERE.

374
00:14:02,509 --> 00:14:04,178
I KNOW.

375
00:14:04,261 --> 00:14:06,305
YOU SHOULD STILL BE
ON "WEST DRIVE,"

376
00:14:06,388 --> 00:14:09,391
BUT YOU GOT YOURSELF FIRED.

377
00:14:09,474 --> 00:14:11,977
NOBODY WANTS TO WORK
WITH YOU NOW,

378
00:14:12,060 --> 00:14:14,062
SO DO WHATEVER IT TAKES
TO MAKE THIS WORK.

379
00:14:16,481 --> 00:14:17,983
(PANTING)

380
00:14:19,693 --> 00:14:21,862
DREW:
WHAT IS GOING ON?

381
00:14:21,945 --> 00:14:24,114
JUST CATCHING SOME RAYS
DURING MY SPARE!

382
00:14:24,198 --> 00:14:25,866
AM I STILL DREAMING?

383
00:14:25,949 --> 00:14:27,451
CLARE:
NOT COOL, DREW!

384
00:14:30,537 --> 00:14:31,413
IF YOU DIDN'T WANNA DO
THE TEXTING AND DRIVING CAMPAIGN

385
00:14:31,496 --> 00:14:32,497
BECAUSE OF ADAM,

386
00:14:32,581 --> 00:14:34,166
YOU COULD'VE SAID SO.

387
00:14:34,249 --> 00:14:35,876
I'M FINE, CLARE.
THEN I'M OFFICIALLY MAD

388
00:14:35,959 --> 00:14:37,920
