A MINI WAVE POOL, TOO?

394
00:14:55,395 --> 00:14:56,480
DREW:
YEAH...

395
00:14:56,563 --> 00:14:58,065
(BELL RINGS)

396
00:15:00,442 --> 00:15:02,611
DUDE, CLARE IS NOT HAPPY.

397
00:15:02,694 --> 00:15:05,531
I KNOW,
IT'S HILARIOUS.

398
00:15:05,614 --> 00:15:06,532
SO DID YOU ORDER
ALL THE SAND?

399
00:15:06,615 --> 00:15:08,116
WHAT? NO.
YOU DID!

400
00:15:09,451 --> 00:15:11,203
LAST NIGHT.

401
00:15:11,286 --> 00:15:11,912
YOU DON'T REMEMBER?

402
00:15:11,995 --> 00:15:13,997
NO!

403
00:15:14,081 --> 00:15:14,831
YOU WERE BANGING AROUND
THE KITCHEN AT LIKE 3:00 A.M.,

404
00:15:14,915 --> 00:15:17,167
SO I GOT UP.

405
00:15:17,251 --> 00:15:18,293
YOU WERE EATING ICE CREAM
AND PLACING AN ORDER ONLINE.

406
00:15:18,377 --> 00:15:19,837
WHAT?! ALL RIGHT,

407
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:22,089
BIANCA SAID THAT
I TALKED TO HER, TOO.

408
00:15:22,172 --> 00:15:23,549
I TOOK THOSE SLEEPING PILLS;
I THOUGHT I SLEPT SO WELL!

409
00:15:23,632 --> 00:15:26,593
DUDE, THOSE PILLS WORK
FOR SOME PEOPLE,

410
00:15:26,677 --> 00:15:29,346
BUT OTHER PEOPLE
GET CRAZY SIDE EFFECTS.

411
00:15:29,429 --> 00:15:30,264
SO I ORDERED THE SAND.

412
00:15:30,347 --> 00:15:32,391
BIG TIME.

413
00:15:32,474 --> 00:15:34,226
GUESS YOU REALLY WANTED
THAT BEACH DANCE.

414
00:15:34,309 --> 00:15:35,352
SO WHAT DO I DO?

415
00:15:35,435 --> 00:15:36,854
PRAY FOR A MIRACLE,

416
00:15:36,937 --> 00:15:37,980
AND HOPE YOU WIN THE VOTE
AT COUNCIL.

417
00:15:38,063 --> 00:15:39,565
OH GOSH...

418
00:15:41,358 --> 00:15:44,653
(GIRLS GIGGLE)

419
00:15:44,736 --> 00:15:46,238
I THINK THERE MIGHT BE A WAY.

420
00:15:48,782 --> 00:15:50,117
IS ANYONE GOING TO THE FASHION
CLUB MEETING TONIGHT?

421
00:15:50,200 --> 00:15:51,535
NO, I'M GONNA WORK
ON A SONG.

422
00:15:51,618 --> 00:15:52,494
I'M THINKING OF STARTING
A NEW BAND.

423
00:15:52,578 --> 00:15:53,829
NO, DON'T LOOK AT ME.

424
00:15:53,912 --> 00:15:54,913
THE ONLY THING I DO
IS BASKETBALL

425
00:15:54,997 --> 00:15:56,623
AND THAT'S 'CAUSE MY DAD
MAKES ME.

426
00:15:56,707 --> 00:15:57,958
TRISTAN:
COOL. I COULD PLAY BASKETBALL.

427
00:15:58,041 --> 00:15:59,918
SERIOUSLY?!

428
00:16:00,002 --> 00:16:01,253
TRISTAN:
MY BROTHER PLAYED.
I COULD DO IT.

429
00:16:01,336 --> 00:16:03,088
