430
00:16:03,172 --> 00:16:04,423
MILES:
YOU MEAN JUMP SHOT?

431
00:16:04,506 --> 00:16:06,133
TRISTAN:
SERIOUSLY?

432
00:16:06,216 --> 00:16:08,969
ZOE:
UM, HEY, DO THEY HAVE
CHEERLEADERS HERE?

433
00:16:09,052 --> 00:16:11,930
