(STARTLED GRUNT)

440
00:16:29,865 --> 00:16:31,867
DREW: HEY.
ZOE: HEY!

441
00:16:31,950 --> 00:16:35,162
DREW: I NEED YOU.
ZOE: I'M SORRY?

442
00:16:35,245 --> 00:16:37,247
DREW:
