WHEN YOU LEAVE?

454
00:17:00,938 --> 00:17:02,731
I WON'T.

455
00:17:02,814 --> 00:17:04,900
I CAN STAY WITH MY GODFATHER
AS LONG AS I WANT.

456
00:17:04,983 --> 00:17:07,152
BUT WHAT ARE YOU
GONNA DO?

457
00:17:07,236 --> 00:17:09,112
I HAVE SCHOOL,
AND A FAMILY, AND-

458
00:17:09,196 --> 00:17:10,364
I'VE LOOKED INTO TRANSFERRING
TO T.U. -

459
00:17:10,447 --> 00:17:11,865
THEY HAVE A GREAT
BIOLOGY DEPARTMENT -

460
00:17:11,949 --> 00:17:13,158
AND I'LL GET A JOB.

461
00:17:13,242 --> 00:17:15,911
WHERE?
HERE.

462
00:17:15,994 --> 00:17:18,455
THEY NEED SOMEONE TO TEACH THEM
HOW TO MAKE COFFEE.

463
00:17:18,539 --> 00:17:20,249
WE CAN DO THIS,
ALLI.

464
00:17:20,332 --> 00:17:21,834
OKAY, AND UM...

465
00:17:23,752 --> 00:17:26,547
WHAT HAPPENS
IF YOU GET JEALOUS AGAIN?

466
00:17:26,630 --> 00:17:29,007
I MEAN, LAST TIME
YOU HURT ME.

467
00:17:29,091 --> 00:17:30,592
