YOU WANT ME TO TURN AWAY
ENTHUSIASTIC

489
00:18:24,062 --> 00:18:26,523
NEW COUNCIL MEMBERS?!

490
00:18:26,607 --> 00:18:28,400
I'D LIKE TO CALL
THIS MEETING TO ORDER.

491
00:18:28,483 --> 00:18:29,610
FIRST UP, THE VOTE ON COUNCIL'S
FIRST EVENT.

492
00:18:29,693 --> 00:18:31,195
CLARE?

493
00:18:32,237 --> 00:18:33,739
(LOUD THUD)

494
00:18:35,490 --> 00:18:38,410
(MUFFLED LAUGHTER)

495
00:18:38,493 --> 00:18:39,411
I'D LIKE TO PROPOSE
AN ANTI-TEXTING

496
00:18:39,494 --> 00:18:41,955
AND DRIVING CAMPAIGN.

497
00:18:42,039 --> 00:18:43,665
WE'LL HANG FOUR THOUSAND
CELL PHONES IN THE FOYER,

498
00:18:43,749 --> 00:18:46,126
ONE FOR EVERY TEEN TEXTING
AND DRIVING DEATH A YEAR.

499
00:18:46,210 --> 00:18:47,711
ALL THOSE IN FAVOUR?

500
00:18:49,588 --> 00:18:52,508
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR, FIVE,
SIX, SEVEN, EIGHT.

501
00:18:52,591 --> 00:18:54,551
AND I PROPOSE A DEGRASSI
"BEACH BASH" DANCE.

502
00:18:54,635 --> 00:18:57,095
SUN, SAND,

503
00:18:57,179 --> 00:18:58,180
AND A FRESH NEW START
FOR EVERYONE THIS YEAR.

504
00:18:58,263 --> 00:18:59,765
ALL IN FAVOUR?

505
00:19:01,183 --> 00:19:04,269
ONE, TWO, THREE, FOUR,
FIVE, SIX, SEVEN, EIGHT...

506
00:19:04,353 --> 00:19:05,854
NINE.
(GAVEL BANGS)

507
00:19:06,647 --> 00:19:07,689
WHO'S READY TO PARTY?

508
00:19:07,773 --> 00:19:09,274
WHAT IS THIS?

509
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,902
IT'S A DEMOCRACY.

510
00:19:13,820 --> 00:19:14,571
WELL, IF THIS IS HOW
YOU WANT TO RUN COUNCIL,

511
00:19:14,655 --> 00:19:16,406
YOU'RE ON YOUR OWN.

512
00:19:16,490 --> 00:19:17,449
AND DREW,
YOU'D BETTER GET SOME SLEEP

513
00:19:17,533 --> 00:19:18,408
BECAUSE IT'S GONNA TAKE
A LOT OF ENERGY

514
00:19:18,492 --> 00:19:19,993
TO WRANGLE
ALL THESE CHILDREN!

515
00:19:21,787 --> 00:19:22,204
I THINK I'LL SLEEP
JUST FINE.

516
00:19:22,287 --> 00:19:24,790
I HOPE SO.

517
00:19:24,873 --> 00:19:26,792
LOOKS LIKE WE HAVE
A DANCE TO PLAN.

518
00:19:26,875 --> 00:19:29,169
FIRST THINGS FIRST,
IF WE'RE GONNA PULL THIS OFF,

519
00:19:29,253 --> 00:19:31,880
I'M GONNA NEED EVERYONE'S
CONTACT INFORMATION.

520
00:19:31,964 --> 00:19:34,174
FEEL FREE TO CALL ME ANYTIME.

521
00:19:34,258 --> 00:19:35,175
WELL, IF YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT PLANNING A DANCE,

522
00:19:35,259 --> 00:19:36,760
I DEFINITELY WILL.

523
00:19:36,844 --> 00:19:39,263
I DON'T YET,
BUT I'M A FAST LEARNER.

524
00:19:39,346 --> 00:19:40,973
(LAUGHS)

525
00:19:41,056 --> 00:19:43,058
